        <name>XV_csc_LookupConfig</name>
        <param>
          <type>UINTPTR</type>
          <declname>BaseAddress</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>XV_csc_LookupConfig - Looks up the configuration for a Color Space Converter (CSC) instance. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>BaseAddress</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The base address of the CSC instance to look up. If 0, returns the first entry.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
This function searches the XV_csc_ConfigTable for an entry matching the provided BaseAddress. If a matching BaseAddress is found, or if BaseAddress is 0 (in which case the first entry is returned), a pointer to the corresponding configuration structure is returned. If no match is found, NULL is returned.</para><para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Pointer to the configuration structure if found.</para></listitem><listitem><para>NULL if no matching configuration is found. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
